NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::SpellingCommonMistakesTests - Release tests for
    common POD spelling mistakes

VERSION
    version 1.000000

SYNOPSIS
    In your dist.ini file:

        [PodSpellingTests]

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following file:

        xt/release/common_spelling.t - a standard Pod::Spell::CommonMistakes test

SEE ALSO
    Please see those modules/websites for more information related to this
    module.

    *   Pod::Spell::CommonMistakes

    *   Test::Pod::Spelling::CommonMistakes

INSTALLATION
    See perlmodinstall for information and options on installing Perl
    modules.

AUTHOR
    Adam Lesperance <lespea@gmail.com>

